---
title: Chorizo, Avocado and Goat's Cheese Salad Serves 2
description: This recipe is super simple and amazingly delicious too. Salad layered with slightly spicy chorizo and juicy cherry tomatoes. Top that off with creamy avocado and creamier goat's cheese for a tasty, easy breezy lunch.
